<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>添加我 WhatsApp</title>
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial;
      background-image: url('arrow-bg.png');
      background-size: cover;
      background-position: top right;
      background-repeat: no-repeat;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: flex-end;
      align-items: center;
      height: 100vh;
      padding: 20px;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    .text-box {
      background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85);
      padding: 18px 24px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .text-box h2 {
      margin: 0 0 12px;
      font-size: 20px;
      color: #000;
    }

    .text-box p {
      font-size: 18px;
      margin: 0;
    }

    .whatsapp-btn {
      background-color: #25D366;
      color: white;
      font-size: 18px;
      padding: 14px 24px;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 10px;
      text-decoration: none;
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 16px;
      width: 90%;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .whatsapp-number {
      font-size: 20px;
      margin-top: 12px;
      color: #111;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="text-box">
    <h2>请点击右上角 “...”</h2>
    <p>选择“在浏览器中打开”</p>
    <div class="whatsapp-number">+1234567890</div>
    <a class="whatsapp-btn" href="https://wa.me/1234567890" target="_blank">点此添加 WhatsApp</a>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
